Gametext: Deploys -2 on Naboo. While on Naboo, once during your control phase may use 1 Force to cancel Maul's immunity to attrition for remainder of turn. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 5 while on Naboo).

Title: Mace Windu, Jedi Master
Gametext: Deploys -2 on Naboo. While on Naboo, once during your control phase may use 1 Force to cancel Maul's immunity to attrition for remainder of turn. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 5 while on Naboo).

Title: Master, Destroyers!
Gametext: USED: Target a character at same site as two of your destroyer droids. For remainder of turn, target may not fire weapons and is power -2. LOST: Lose 1 Force to take up to three non-unique destroyer droids into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Multi Troop Transport
Gametext: May add 1 pilot and 7 passengers. Your battle droids may move from this site for free. Immune to attrition < 3.

Title: Naboo Celebration
Gametext: Deploy on table. If Amidala at a Theed Palace site (or Boss Nass at an exterior Naboo site), opponent's cards with ability deploy +2 there. Once during battle at a Naboo site, if you just drew a Gungan or Royal Naboo Security for battle destiny, opponent loses 1 Force.

Title: Naboo Occupation
Gametext: Deploy on table. During your draw phase, may use 3 Force: until end of next turn, opponent generates no Force at Naboo sites you control with a battle droid. Place Effect in Lost Pile if you have no battle droids on Naboo. (Immune to Alter.)

Title: Naboo: Boss Nass' Chambers
DarkSideText: Opponent may not Force drain here. Immune to Revolution.
LightSideText: Once per game may take Boss Nass into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Naboo: Otoh Gunga Entrance
DarkSideText: Cards with ability (except Gungans) deploy +4 to underwater sites. Immune to Revolution.
LightSideText: Your Gungans deploy -1 here and move from here for free. You may not Force drain here.

Title: Naboo: Theed Palace Hallway
DarkSideText: If your battle droid present, Force drain +1 here.
LightSideText: Once per game, may take Ascension Guns into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Naboo: Theed Palace Hallway
DarkSideText: Once per game, may deploy a battle droid here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.
LightSideText: Force drain -1 here.

Title: No Giben Up, General Jar Jar!
Gametext: If you just lost a Gungan from table, place him in your hand. OR If Jar Jar and Tarpals are in a battle together, add two battle destiny.

Title: Nothing Can Get Through Our Shield
Gametext: Non-pilot characters aboard starships are forfeit -4. Whenever a player's starship is 'hit', that player loses 1 Force (2 if starship was hit by Droid Starfighter Laser Cannons). At systems where you have only [Trade Federation] starships, all of those starships are immune to attrition < 4. At sites related to a system you occupy, your battle destinies may not be canceled by opponent.

Title: Nute Gunray, Neimoidian Viceroy
Gametext: Your [Presence] droids and AATs are destiny +1 if drawn for battle or weapon destiny. Once per turn, may take Take Them Away into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < X, where X = twice the number of [Presence] droids present.

Title: Nute Gunray, Neimoidian Viceroy
Gametext: Your [Presence] droids and AATs are destiny +1 if drawn for battle or weapon destiny. Once per turn, may take Take Them Away into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < X, where X = twice the number of [Presence] droids present.

Title: Officer Dolphe
Gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While piloting Bravo 2, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise, and opponent's battle destiny draws are -2 at same system.

Title: Officer Ellberger
Gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything she pilots. While piloting Bravo 5 and at same system as a droid starfighter, adds one destiny to attrition only.

Title: Officer Perosei
Gametext: Once during your deploy phase, may use 1 Force to relocate Perosei to an adjacent Naboo site. While with a Republic character during battle, may place Perosei out of play to add 5 to your total power this battle.

Title: OOM-9
Gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. May add or subtract one from a just drawn Energy Shell weapon destiny draw here. While at Battle Plains, twice per game may take Open Fire! or Cease Fire! into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Open Fire!
Gametext: Deploy on your AAT. Once during your control phase may use 3 Force to fire your AAT Laser Cannon on this AAT for free.

Title: OWO-1 With Backup
Gametext: Requires +2 Force to use landspeed. Power +1 for each of opponent's Jedi present. While with a battle droid at a site, draws two battle destiny if unable to otherwise. Opponent's Force drains are -1 at adjacent sites.

Title: Panaka, Protector Of The Queen
Gametext: Deploys for free to a Naboo site. While with Amidala at a Naboo site, opponent may not target Amidala with weapons. While on Naboo, immune to attrition < 5.

Title: Panaka, Protector Of The Queen
Gametext: Deploys for free to a Naboo site. While with Amidala at a Naboo site, opponent may not target Amidala with weapons. While on Naboo, immune to attrition < 5.

Title: Proton Torpedoes
Gametext: Use 1 Force to deploy on your N-1 starfighter. May target a starship using 1 force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny > defense value. While on Bravo Fighter and you are attempting to 'blow away' Blockade Flagship, adds 2 to your total.

Title: Queen Amidala
Gametext: Deploys -1 to Naboo. Amidala and your other Republic characters present are defense value +2, and immune to You Are Beaten, Sniper, and attrition < 3.

Title: Queen Amidala
Gametext: Deploys -1 to Naboo. Amidala and your other Republic characters present are defense value +2, and immune to You Are Beaten, Sniper, and attrition < 3.

Title: Qui-Gon Jinn With Lightsaber
Gametext: Adds one battle destiny if with Maul. Permanent weapon is •Qui-Gon Jinn's Lightsaber (may target a character or creature for free; draw two destiny; target 'hit', and its forfeit = 0, if total destiny > defense value).

Title: Rayno Vaca
Gametext: Your characters may move from here using their landspeed for free. During your control phase, may place Vaca in Used Pile to take Lana Dobreed into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Rep Been
Gametext: Deploys -1 to an underwater site. While at Boss Nass' Chambers: your Force generation here is +1 for each Gungan present, and once per game, may take an underwater site into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Ric Olié, Bravo Leader
Gametext: Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. While piloting during a battle at a system where you have two piloted Bravo Squadron starfighters, adds two battle destiny.

Title: Rolling, Rolling, Rolling
Gametext: Take any non-unique destroyer droid into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR During your deploy phase, relocate your destroyer droid to an adjacent site.

Title: Royal Naboo Security Officer
Gametext: Power -1 while not on Naboo. While you have at least three other non-unique Royal Naboo Security Officers at related Naboo sites, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise.

Title: Rune Haako, Legal Counsel
Gametext: While at Theed Palace Throne Room, your attrition against opponent in battles at same and related Naboo sites is +X, where X = number of battle droids present at that site. While with a battle droid, Haako is power and defense value +2.

Title: Rune Haako, Legal Counsel
Gametext: While at Theed Palace Throne Room, your attrition against opponent in battles at same and related Naboo sites is +X, where X = number of battle droids present at that site. While with a battle droid, Haako is power and defense value +2.

Title: Senate Hovercam
Gametext: Deploy on Galactic Senate. While you have a senate majority, your Force generation here is +3, and your Force generation at Coruscant locations is immune to This Place Can Be A Little Rough. Place Effect in Lost Pile if opponent controls this location.

Title: Senate Hovercam
Gametext: Deploy on Galactic Senate. Amidala is politics +1 here. While you have a senate majority, your Force generation here is +3. Place Effect in Lost Pile if opponent controls this location.

Title: Sil Unch
Gametext: Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. While aboard a battleship, that battleship is immune to attrition < 4 and draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise.

Title: Single Trooper Aerial Platform
Gametext: May add 1 pilot. May move as a 'react.' When piloted by a battle droid, vehicle and pilot are immune to attrition < 4. Pilot's power = 0. If lost, character aboard may "jump off" (disembark).

Title: SSA-1015
Gametext: While with an opponent's Jedi, your other battle droids present are power +1. Opponent's Jedi are deploy +4 to same site. While with another battle droid at a site, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise.

Title: SSA-306
Gametext: At same site, opponent's spies and smugglers are deploy +4 and may not apply their ability toward drawing battle destiny. While with another battle droid at a site, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise.

Title: SSA-719
Gametext: While with another battle droid, power +3. If with a battle droid on Naboo and you just verified opponent's Reserve Deck, may lose 2 Force to search that Reserve Deck and place one card you find there out of play.

Title: STAP Blaster Cannons
Gametext: Deploy on your STAP. Vehicle is power +3. May target a character, creature or vehicle for free. Draw two destiny and choose one. Target hit if destiny +2 > defense value.

Title: Steady, Steady
Gametext: Deploy on table. If you have two Gungans with different card titles at Battle Plains, your Force drains are +2 there. While two underwater sites on table, your Gungans and creature vehicles are immune to attrition < 4 where your Fambaa is present. (Immune to Alter.)

Title: Take Them Away
Gametext: USED: Subtract one from a just drawn battle destiny. LOST: During opponent's control phase, use X Force to 'break cover' of an opponent's undercover spy at same site as your battle droid or Neimoidian, where X = spy's deploy cost.

Title: Take This!
Gametext: If you are about to draw weapon destiny for Proton Torpedoes, instead draw 3 and choose 1. OR For rest of turn, add 2 to any attempt to 'blow away' Blockade Flagship. OR Take Proton Torpedoes or Bravo Fighter into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Tank Commander
Gametext: Adds 3 to the power of any AAT he pilots. While piloting an AAT, forfeit +2, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise, and your other [Presence] droids at this site are immune to attrition < 4.

Title: The Deflector Shield Is Too Strong
Gametext: Landed starfighters and vehicles aboard starships are forfeit = 0. Once during your control phase may target your droid starfighter and opponent's starfighter present at same system. Both players draw destiny. You add your starfighter's power and maneuver. Opponent adds starfighter's power. Starship with lowest total is lost.

Title: There They Are!
Gametext: If a battle was just initiated, your non-unique battle droids are each power +1 for remainder of battle. (Immune to Sense if battle at a Naboo site.) OR Take a non-unique battle droid or non-unique droid starfighter into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: They Win This Round
Gametext: If opponent just Force drained you at a location, deploy on that location. Opponent's Force drains here are +1. Your battle destiny draws here are +1. If you control this location, may place Immediate Effect in Used Pile to retrieve 4 Force. (Immune to Control.)

Title: This Is Not Good
Gametext: USED: For remainder of turn, subtract 2 from any attempt to 'blow away' Blockade Flagship. LOST: During any deploy phase, use 3 Force to target any starship at same system as your battleship. Target is hyperspeed = 0 until end of turn.

Title: Trade Federation Landing Craft
Gametext: May add 2 pilots and 6 vehicles. Deploys and moves like a starfighter. While at a site, once during your deploy phase may take an MTT into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Trade Federation Tactics
Gametext: Use 2 Force to target a starship at same system as your [Trade Federation] starship armed with a weapon. Target is forfeit = 0 until end of turn. OR During battle, add X to your total power, where X = armor of one of your [Trade Federation] starships in that battle.

Title: TT-6
Gametext: May add 7 passengers. Once per turn, may deploy a battle droid leader to same site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 5 if your AAT or STAP present).

Title: TT-9
Gametext: May add 4 passengers and 3 STAPs. Once per turn, may deploy a STAP to same site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 5 if your AAT or STAP present).

Title: We Didn't Hit It
Gametext: Deploy on table. Your Force generation is +1 at systems you control. Opponent's non-unique starfighters are deploy +1 (or +2 to a system you occupy). (Immune to Alter.)

Title: We Don't Have Time For This
Gametext: If Amidala and Panaka are in a battle together, add two battle destiny. OR Target an interior Naboo site where opponent has a battle droid. Draw destiny. If destiny > number of battle droids at that site, one of them is lost (opponent's choice).

Title: We Have A Plan
Gametext:
While this side up, you lose no more than 2 Force to any Force drain. Your [Republic] starships are power +2 and immunity to attrition of [Trade Federation] starships is canceled. If opponent just drew a battle destiny greater than three, you may use 1 Force to cancel that battle destiny. During your control phase, opponent loses 2 Force for each battleground site you control with Amidala or Panaka.
Flip this card if opponent controls Theed Palace Throne Room.

Title: They Will Be Lost And Confused
Gametext:
Deploy Theed Palace Throne Room, Theed Palace Hallway, and Theed Palace Courtyard.
For remainder of game, you may not deploy cards with ability except [Episode 1] Jedi, aliens, [Episode 1] vehicles, Republic characters, and [Republic] starships. Your Destiny is suspended. You lose no Force to Vengeance Of The Dark Prince.
While this side up, you may not deploy characters to interior Naboo sites. Once per turn, may activate 1 Force.
Flip this card if you control Theed Palace Throne Room (with Amidala there).

Title: We're Hit, Artoo
Gametext: Once during battle, target a participating starfighter present with your droid starfighter. Draw destiny. If destiny > target's defense value, target 'hit,' OR If opponent's starfighter was just 'hit' where your droid starfighter is present, activate up to 4 Force.

Title: Wesa Gotta Grand Army
Gametext: USED: Take a Fambaa, Battle Plains, or Boss Nass' Chambers into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Subtract one from any just drawn weapon destiny. LOST: Target an opponent's undercover spy with your Gungan. Target is lost.

Title: Wesa Ready To Do Our-sa Part
Gametext: Deploy on table. If your Gungan was just lost from a site, may place him here. Once per battle, may place one of your Gungans here out of play to add 4 to your total power during that battle.

Title: Whoooo!
Gametext: Take a unique (•)N-1 starfighter into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR If a battle was just initiated at a system where opponent has a droid starfighter, all droid starfighters at that system are power -1 for remainder of turn.

Title: 2-1B (Too-Onebee)
Gametext: Once per turn, your non-droid character lost from same site may go to your Used Pile rather than your Lost Pile. Subtracts 2 from X on your Bacta Tank.

Title: A Dark Time For The Rebellion
Gametext: If opponent just deployed a planet site, deploy the related system from your Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Admiral Ozzel
Gametext: Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots. Subtracts 1 from deploy cost of each of your capital starships at same system. Lost if Vader on table and opponent 'reacts' to same location as Ozzel.

Title: Anakin's Lightsaber
Gametext: Deploy on your Skywalker of ability > 3. May add 1 to Force drain where present. May target a character or creature for free. Draw two destiny. Target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if total destiny > defense value.

Title: Artillery Remote
Gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy on your warrior. Your artillery weapons anywhere on same planet may fire without a warrior present. Also, once during each of your control phases, one of your artillery weapons on same planet may be fired.

Title: AT-AT Cannon
Gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy on your AT-AT. May target a starfighter (use 3 as defense value), character, creature or vehicle at same or adjacent site using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Add 1 if targeting a character or creature, 2 if a vehicle. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.

Title: AT-AT Driver
Gametext: Adds 2 to power of any combat vehicle he pilots (3 if combat vehicle is an AT-AT).

Title: Atgar Laser Cannon
Gametext: Deploy on an exterior planet site. Your warrior present may target a vehicle at same or adjacent site using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Target crashes if destiny +2 > armor. Target hit if destiny +1 > maneuver.

Title: Attack Pattern Delta
Gametext: If a battle was just initiated at a site, identify your lead T-47 there. For remainder of turn, each other T-47 at same site is power +1, is immune to attrition and cannot be targeted by weapons.

Title: Bacta Tank
Gametext: Use 4 Force to deploy on your side of table. A non-droid character you just lost may be placed here. Holds one 'patient' at a time. During your deploy phase, may use X Force to bring 'patient' to hand, where X = deploy cost of 'patient.'

Title: Blizzard 1
Gametext: May add 2 pilots and 8 passengers. Immune to attrition < 4. Landspeed may not be increased. When using AT-AT Cannon to Target The Main Generator, adds 1 to total.

Title: Blizzard 2
Gametext: May add 1 pilot and 8 passengers. Immune to attrition < 4. Landspeed may not be increased. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2.

Title: Blizzard Scout 1
Gametext: May add 1 pilot or passenger. May move as a 'react.' Power +1 at any Hoth site. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1.

Title: Blizzard Walker
Gametext: May add 2 pilots and 8 passengers. Immune to attrition < 4. Landspeed may not be increased.

Title: Breached Defenses
Gametext: If an Imperial just moved to an Echo site, deploy on your side of table. While you have presence at an Echo site, your total power is +1 in battles at Hoth sites.

Title: Cal Alder
Gametext: Power +1 at Defensive Perimeter. Your vehicles move for free if moving toward same site as Cal.

Title: Captain Lennox
Gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (3 if starship is Tyrant). When on a Star Destroyer, may use its tractor beam once during each of your control phases.

Title: Captain Piett
Gametext: Power +1 when at same site as Vader. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (3 if starship is Executor). May use 1 Force to take one Probe Droid into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Cold Feet
Gametext: Target a character at any marker site. Draw destiny. If site under "nighttime conditions," add 2 to destiny draw. If total destiny > ability, character may not move for remainder of turn.

Title: Collapsing Corridor
Gametext: If you just moved an AT-AT to innermost marker, target one underground site on Hoth. Draw destiny. Target 'collapsed' if destiny > marker number.

Title: Commander Luke Skywalker
Gametext: Deploys only on Hoth. Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Rogue 1, also adds 2 to maneuver. Immune to attrition < 3. Adds 1 to forfeit of each other Rogue Squadron pilot or gunner at same Hoth site.

Title: ComScan Detection
Gametext: If opponent just moved a character, vehicle or starship as a 'react' to a location, you may immediately move one vehicle or starship, if within range, to that location. (as a regular move)

Title: Concussion Grenade
Gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy on your warrior. May 'throw' at same or adjacent site. Draw destiny. All characters, weapons and devices with that destiny number present at that site are lost. (Only your warrior is lost if destiny = 0.) Concussion Grenade also lost.

Title: Crash Landing
Gametext: If you have a piloted AT-AT present at a site, target opponent's non-creature vehicle present at same or adjacent exterior site. Draw destiny. If that AT-AT has a vehicle weapon, add 1 to destiny draw. Target 'crashes' if total destiny > 3.

Title: Dack Ralter
Gametext: Adds 1 to weapon destiny draws of anything he is aboard as a passenger (adds 3 if aboard Rogue 1 or with Luke).

Title: Dark Dissension
Gametext: USED: Cancel Dark Collaboration or Lone Pilot. LOST: If two Imperials each with ability > 2 are in a battle together, use 2 Force to draw two destiny. Subtract that amount from opponent's attrition and total power.

Title: Death Mark
Gametext: Use 3 Force to deploy on any exterior planet site. Target an opponent's smuggler. Each turn opponent must lose 1 Force at beginning of opponent's control phase. Utinni Effect canceled when reached by target (target goes to Used Pile).

Title: Death Squadron
Gametext: Deploy on any system. Adds X to total power of your starships at that system, where X = number of your starships present. Your troopers and combat vehicles may shuttle to related sites for free.

Title: Debris Zone
Gametext: If an AT-AT, an AT-ST, Jabba's Sail Barge or Planet Defender Ion Cannon has just been lost at a site, draw destiny. All cards with that destiny number at that site are lost.

Title: Deflector Shield Generators
Gametext: Use 3 Force to deploy on your Star Destroyer. Adds 2 to armor. If starship has immunity to attrition, also adds 2 to immunity.

Title: Derek 'Hobbie' Klivian
Gametext: Power +2 when at same site as Biggs. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (3 if a Star Destroyer is at same location). When piloting Rogue 4, also adds 2 to maneuver.

Title: Direct Hit
Gametext: Add X to one weapon destiny (before weapon destiny is drawn) when targeting a combat vehicle. USED: X = 1. LOST: X = 3.

Title: Disarming Creature
Gametext: If you have a character with a weapon at same site as any creature, deploy on that creature during any deploy phase. Creature is Disarmed (each time ferocity is calculated, draw destiny, subtract that amount). (Immune to Control.)

Title: Dual Laser Cannon
Gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy on your T-47. May target a character, creature or vehicle using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Subtract 1 if targeting a character or creature. Add 2 if targeting a vehicle. Target hit if total destiny > defense value.

Title: Echo Base Operations
Gametext: Deploy on Main Power Generators if you occupy at least three Echo sites. At every system location, your deploy is -1, your Force drains are +2 and your total power is +3 in battles. Effect canceled if opponent occupies five Hoth sites. (Immune to Alter.)

Title: Echo Base Trooper
Gametext: Deploys only on Hoth. Power -1 when not at a Hoth site.

Title: Echo Base Trooper Officer
Gametext: Deploys only on Hoth. Echo Base Troopers deploy -1 to same site. Your troopers may move to same Hoth site as a 'react.'

Title: Echo Trooper Backpack
Gametext: Deploy on your trooper. May use any number of weapons and devices. Trooper is immune to attrition < 3 when at a planet site.

Title: EG-4 (Eegee-Four)
Gametext: Adds 1 to power of each of your droids present, except power droids. * Destiny equals zero, but if drawn as a battle destiny where you have less power than opponent, your total power present is doubled (once per battle).

Title: Electro-Rangefinder
Gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy on your AT-AT Cannon. It may fire at targets two sites away. Also, when used to Target The Main Generator, adds 1 to total.

Title: Evacuation Control
Gametext: Deploy on your war room. Once during each of your move phases, your Planet Defender Ion Cannon at same planet may fire. Also, each of your medium transports at same planet is hyperspeed +2, is immune to attrition < 3 and may move for free.

Title: E-web Blaster
Gametext: Deploy on any site. May be moved with two warriors for 1 additional Force. Your warrior present may target a starfighter (use 5 as defense value), character, creature or vehicle using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny +1 > defense value.

Title: Exhaustion
Gametext: Opponent must lose 1 Force for each of opponent's missing characters on table. OR Select one missing character under "nighttime conditions" to be lost.

Title: Exposure
Gametext: Use X Force during your control phase, where X = the total number of characters present or missing at exterior marker sites under "nighttime conditions." Those characters are lost.

Title: Fall Back!
Gametext: If opponent just initiated a battle at an exterior site with more than double your total power, use 1 Force to cancel the battle and move all your characters there to an adjacent site (for free) where the opponent has no presence.

Title: Frostbite
Gametext: Deploy on Hoth system. At the end of each player's turn, for every character that player has present at a marker site under "nighttime conditions," that player must lose 1 Force (2 if character is missing).

Title: Frostbite
Gametext: Deploy on Hoth system. At the end of each player's turn, for every character that player has present at a marker site under "nighttime conditions," that player must lose 1 Force (2 if character is missing).

Title: Frozen Dinner
Gametext: Deploy on opponent's character alone at Wampa Cave. Character is power = 0 and may not move. May be canceled if opponent has a lightsaber or total ability > 4 present. If character eaten by a creature, cumulatively adds 2 to ferocity.

Title: Furry Fury
Gametext: USED: Cancel Wookiee Roar, Han's Back or Life Debt. LOST: If Han and Chewie are in a battle together, draw two destiny. Subtract total from opponent's attrition and total power (cannot fall below zero).

Title: FX-10 (Effex-ten)
Gametext: Once per turn, your 'hit' non-droid character at same or adjacent site may go to your Used Pile rather than your Lost Pile.

Title: FX-7 (Effex-Seven)
Gametext: Once per turn, your 'hit' non-droid character at same or adjacent site may go to your Used Pile rather than your Lost Pile. Cumulatively subtracts 2 from X on your Bacta Tank.

Title: General Carlist Rieekan
Gametext: Adds 1 to power of each of your Rebels present at same Hoth site. May use 1 Force to cancel Death Squadron. While at an Echo site, opponent must occupy an additional Hoth site to cancel Echo Base Operations.

Title: General Veers
Gametext: Power +1 when at same site as Admiral Ozzel. Adds 1 to power of each Imperial at same Hoth site. Adds 3 to power of any combat vehicle he pilots. On Blizzard 1, also adds 1 to armor and draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.

Title: Golan Laser Battery
Gametext: Deploy on any exterior planet site. Your warrior present may target a creature, character or vehicle at same or adjacent site using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Add 2 if targeting a creature or character. Target hit if destiny > defense value.

Title: He Hasn't Come Back Yet
Gametext: During your control phase, target any character alone at your exterior planet sites (except a docking bay). Draw destiny. Target is missing if destiny +3 > ability.

Title: High Anxiety
Gametext: If an opponent's character with ability > 2 has just become missing, deploy on a Rebel with ability > 2 on same planet. Rebel may not participate in battle. Immediate Effect canceled if missing character is found or lost.

Title: Hoth
DarkSideText: If you control, for each of your starships here, your total power is +1 in battles at Hoth sites.
LightSideText: If you control, for each of your starships here, your total power is +1 in battles at Hoth sites.

Title: Hoth
DarkSideText: If you control, for each of your starships here, your total power is +1 in battles at Hoth sites.
LightSideText: If you control, for each of your starships here, your total power is +1 in battles at Hoth sites.

Title: Hoth Survival Gear
Gametext: Deploy on your Rebel or warrior. While on Hoth, that character is power and forfeit +1 and is immune to Frostbite, Exposure and Ice Storm.

Title: Hoth: Defensive Perimeter (3rd Marker)
DarkSideText: Force drain +1 here. Add 1 to each of your weapon destiny draws here.
LightSideText: Your troopers are forfeit -1 here

Title: Hoth: Defensive Perimeter (3rd Marker)
DarkSideText: Force drain +1 here.
LightSideText: Your Echo Base Troopers deploy -1 here. Force drain +1 here.

Title: Hoth: Echo Command Center (War Room)
DarkSideText: Add 1 to total of Commence Primary Ignition when targeting the Hoth system.
LightSideText: If you control, your starship movement from Hoth sites to the Hoth system is free.

Title: Hoth: Echo Command Center (War Room)
DarkSideText: Force drain -1 here. If you initiate a battle here, add one battle destiny.
LightSideText: If you control, with X leaders here, your total power is +X in battles at Hoth locations.

Title: Hoth: Echo Corridor
DarkSideText: If you occupy, you may raise all of your converted Hoth locations to the top.

Title: Hoth: Echo Corridor
LightSideText: If you control, once per turn, may use 4 Force to raise a converted Hoth site to the top.

Title: Hoth: Echo Docking Bay
DarkSideText: Your docking bay transit from here requires 2 Force.
LightSideText: Your docking bay transit from here requires 1 Force.

Title: Hoth: Echo Docking Bay
DarkSideText: Your docking bay transit from here requires 3 Force. Your transit to here requires +4 Force.
LightSideText: Your docking bay transit from here requires 1 Force.

Title: Hoth: Echo Med Lab
DarkSideText: If you control with an Imperial present, Force drain +1 here.
LightSideText: Once per turn, if you deploy a medical droid, it is deploy -2.

Title: Hoth: Ice Plains (5th Marker)
DarkSideText: During your move phase, you may move (for free) between here and Mountains.
LightSideText: If Main Power Generators on table, Force drain -1 here.

Title: Hoth: Main Power Generators (1st Marker)
DarkSideText: "Hoth Energy Shield Rules" in effect. If "blown away," Light Side loses 8 Force.
LightSideText: "Hoth Energy Shield Rules" in effect. Your artillery weapons here are powered.

Title: Hoth: North Ridge (4th Marker)
DarkSideText: Your AT-ATs move to here for free.

Title: Hoth: North Ridge (4th Marker)
DarkSideText: This site does not count when calculating Epic Events.
LightSideText: This site does not count when calculating Epic Events.

Title: Hoth: Snow Trench (2nd Marker)
DarkSideText: If you control, Force generation +1 for you here.
LightSideText: Add 1 to each of your weapon destiny draws here.

Title: Hoth: Wampa Cave (7th Marker)
DarkSideText: Your Wampas deploy free here.
LightSideText: If Main Power Generators on table, Force drain -1 here.

Title: I Thought They Smelled Bad On The Outside
Gametext: Sacrifice (lose) your creature vehicle to protect one character present from Exposure, Ice Storm, Frostbite and Gravel Storm for remainder of turn. (Two characters may be protected if sacrificing a ronto.) OR Double Tzizvvt's power until he moves.

Title: I'd Just As Soon Kiss A Wookiee
Gametext: Use 3 Force to place an opponent's just deployed character, starship, vehicle, weapon, or device in opponent's hand. On opponent's next turn, that card (or one card of same title) may deploy for free.

Title: Ice Storm
Gametext: Deploy at outermost marker. All characters present at same exterior site are missing. Each turn, during your control phase, storm moves to next marker, reversing direction if at innermost marker. Mobile Effect lost when moved beyond outermost marker.

Title: Ice Storm
Gametext: Deploy at outermost marker. All characters present at same exterior site are missing. Each turn, during your control phase, storm moves to next marker, reversing direction if at innermost marker. Mobile Effect lost when moved beyond outermost marker.

Title: Image Of The Dark Lord
Gametext: Use 4 Force to deploy at any site if opponent is generating at least 3 Force more than you. At that site, adjacent sites and same site as Vader, players activate Force only if they have presence.

Title: Imperial Domination
Gametext: Deploy on any location. Whenever you control this location during your control phase but do not Force drain here, opponent generates no Force here on opponent's next turn.

Title: Imperial Gunner
Gametext: Adds 1 to weapon destiny draws of anything he is aboard as a passenger.

Title: Imperial Supply
Gametext: USED: Lose 1 Force to activate 2 Force. LOST: Lose 1 Force to activate 4 Force.

Title: Infantry Mine
Gametext: Deploy at same exterior site as your mining droid. 'Explodes' if a character deploys or moves (without using a vehicle or starfighter) to or across same site. Draw destiny. Character lost if destiny +2 > defense value. Infantry Mine is also lost.

Title: Infantry Mine
Gametext: Deploy at same exterior site as your mining droid. 'Explodes' if a character deploys or moves (without using a vehicle or starfighter) to or across same site. Draw destiny. Character lost if destiny +2 > defense value. Infantry Mine is also lost.

Title: It Can Wait
Gametext: Use 3 Force to place an opponent's just deployed character, starship, vehicle, weapon, or device in opponent's hand. On opponent's next turn, that card (or one card of same title) may deploy for free.

Title: Jeroen Webb
Gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When in battle with a Rebel leader, subtracts 1 from opponent's total battle destiny.

Title: K-3PO (Kay-Threepio)
Gametext: May initiate battle and be battled. K-3PO is power +1 for each of your other droids at same Hoth or Yavin 4 site. Functions as a leader if present with another of your droids.

Title: Lieutenant Cabbel
Gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. On Tyrant, also adds 1 to armor. When in battle with an Imperial leader, subtracts 1 from opponent's total battle destiny.

Title: Lightsaber Deficiency
Gametext: Cancel Lightsaber Proficiency. OR Target a character with ability < 4 using a lightsaber in a battle or a Force drain. Draw destiny. Target lost if destiny > ability. Lightsaber lost if destiny = ability.

Title: Lucky Shot
Gametext: Add X to one weapon destiny (before weapon destiny is drawn) when targeting a combat vehicle. USED: X = 1. LOST: X = 3.

Title: Major Bren Derlin
Gametext: While on Hoth, opponent may not 'react' to any Echo site, and Derlin may use 1 Force to cancel Breached Defenses. While at Cantina, power +1 and may use 1 Force to cancel Local Trouble.

Title: Medium Repeating Blaster Cannon
Gametext: Deploy on a site. May be moved by two warriors for 1 additional Force. Your warrior present may target up to two characters or creatures at same or adjacent site using 2 Force. Draw two destiny. Target(s) hit if total destiny > total defense value.

Title: Medium Transport
Gametext: Deploys and moves like a starfighter. May add 1 pilot, 4 passengers and 1 vehicle. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1.

Title: Meteor Impact?
Gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy on an exterior planet site. Target a character on same planet. Character may not leave planet or move away from Utinni Effect. Utinni Effect canceled when reached by target.

Title: Mournful Roar
Gametext: Deploy on Chewie if Han was just lost or just became missing. Opponent cannot play Let The Wookiee Win or Wookiee Roar. Opponent must also lose 1 Force at end of every player's turn. If Han on table, Effect canceled.

Title: Nice Of You Guys To Drop By
Gametext: Send one of your missing characters at same site as one of your piloted or driven vehicles to your Used Pile. OR Cancel any attempt by one character to 'hide' from a battle.

Title: Oh, Switch Off
Gametext: Cancel an attempt by opponent to target your droid to be stolen, 'hit' or lost. Droid is protected from all such attempts for remainder of turn. OR Switch OFF any binary droid for remainder of turn.

Title: One More Pass
Gametext: If you are about to draw power harpoon weapon destiny, add ability of one pilot aboard same vehicle.

Title: Ord Mantell
DarkSideText: Your Bounty Hunters are deploy -2 here.

Title: Ord Mantell
DarkSideText: Each of your bounty hunter pilots add an additional 1 to power of starships they pilot here.
LightSideText: If you control, each of opponent's bounty hunters is forfeit -2.

Title: Our First Catch Of The Day
Gametext: Add 2 to a tractor beam destiny draw. OR Cancel The First Transport Is Away! or Hyper Escape.

Title: Perimeter Scan
Gametext: Use 1 Force to peek at any one card which is face-down at a location. OR Use 1 Force to peek at opponent's hand. You may move each droid spy and Infantry Mine you find there to opponent's Used Pile. OR Cancel Probe Telemetry.

Title: Planet Defender Ion Cannon
Gametext: Deploy on an exterior Rebel Base site. During a battle at related system, may target a capital starship there using 2 Force. Draw destiny. If destiny +3 > armor, all starship weapons aboard target are lost, power = 0 and hyperspeed = 0.

Title: Portable Fusion Generator
Gametext: Deploy on your warrior. When that warrior fires a blaster rifle or artillery weapon, adds 1 to each of that weapon's destiny draws. Also, may add 1 to power of one droid present.

Title: Power Harpoon
Gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy on your combat or shuttle vehicle. May target an AT-AT or AT-ST for 1 Force. Draw destiny. Target crashes if destiny + your vehicle's maneuver > 8. Your vehicle 'crashes' if destiny = 0.

Title: Probe Antennae
Gametext: Deploy on your Probe Droid. Adds 2 to X for that droid. OR Use 1 Force to deploy on one of your other droids. When at a site you control, once during each of your control phases, you may peek at one card randomly selected from opponent's hand.

Title: Probe Droid
Gametext: Deploys only if a Star Destroyer on table. Once during each of your control phases, may peek at X cards randomly selected from opponent's hand, where X = number of (Light Side Force icon) icons at same site. May Force drain, initiate battle and be battled.

Title: Probe Droid Laser
Gametext: Deploy on your probe droid. May target an artillery weapon (use 5 as defense value), character or creature for free. Draw destiny. Artillery weapon lost if destiny > defense value. Character or creature hit if destiny > defense value.

Title: Probe Telemetry
Gametext: Use 2 Force to choose X non-unique cards in any Lost Pile and place them out of play, where X = number of probe droids on table. OR If your only character on a planet is a probe droid, your cards deploy -1 to related sites for remainder of turn.

Title: R2 Sensor Array
Gametext: Deploy on your R-unit droid. Your characters present may move as a 'react' from a creature attack. Also, adds 3 to search party destiny draws at same and adjacent sites.

Title: R-3PO (Ar-Threepio)
Gametext: Once during each of your control phases, for each opponent's spy present, opponent must lose 1 Force (2 if spy is a droid or is Undercover, 4 if both).

Title: R5-M2 (Arfive-Emmtoo)
Gametext: When aboard a capital starship, adds 1 to power and hyperspeed and that starship is immune to attrition < 3.

Title: Rebel Scout
Gametext: May move as a 'react' (for free) to a battle where you have a Rebel of ability > 2 or a leader.

Title: Responsibility Of Command
Gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy on any war room at a Rebel Base. Target a Rebel with forfeit > 4 or an opponent's leader. Opponent may not initiate a battle or a Force drain at same location as target. Utinni Effect canceled when reached by target.

Title: Rogue 1
Gametext: May add 2 pilots or passengers. Immune to attrition < 3 if Luke piloting. May move as a 'react' only to Hoth sites.

Title: Rogue 2
Gametext: May add 2 pilots or passengers. Immune to attrition < 3 if Zev piloting. May add 2 to search party destiny draw if all pilots aboard are part of that search party.

Title: Rogue 3
Gametext: May add 2 pilots or passengers. Immune to attrition < 3 if Wedge piloting. May move as a 'react' only to Hoth sites.

Title: Rogue Gunner
Gametext: Adds 1 to weapon destiny draws of anything he is aboard as a passenger.

Title: Romas "Lock" Navander
Gametext: Adds 1 to power and maneuver of anything he pilots. Opponent may not 'react' to or from same location.

Title: Rug Hug
Gametext: If Luke and Chewie are in a battle together, you may add two battle destiny. OR If you have a Rebel and an alien in a battle together, you may add 4 to power only.

Title: Scruffy-Looking Nerf Herder
Gametext: USED: Cancel Solo Han, Warrior's Courage or I Know. LOST: If Han and Leia are in a battle together, draw two destiny. Subtract that amount from opponent's attrition and total power.

Title: Self-Destruct Mechanism
Gametext: Lose a droid to cancel all attrition against you at same site this turn. OR Retarget an opponent's weapon to one of your droids at same site as target. If droid is 'hit', use original target's forfeit number.

Title: Shawn Valdez
Gametext: Whenever you just initiated a battle at same site as Shawn, your troopers at adjacent sites who have not already battled this turn may immediately move to same site (as a regular move).

Title: Silence Is Golden
Gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy on your side of table. Neither player may move or deploy cards as a 'react' to a location where a droid is present. May be canceled by Scomp Link Access.

Title: Snowspeeder
Gametext: May add 1 pilot or passenger. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1. May move as a 'react' to Hoth sites.

Title: Snowtrooper
Gametext: Deploys only on Hoth. Power -1 when not at a Hoth site.

Title: Snowtrooper Officer
Gametext: Deploys only on Hoth. Snowtroopers deploy -1 to same site. Your troopers may move to same Hoth site as a 'react.'

Title: Stalker
Gametext: May add 6 pilots, 8 passengers, 2 vehicles and 4 TIEs. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. Probe droids deploy free to sites related to same system.

Title: Stop Motion
Gametext: Target one creature vehicle at any marker site. Draw destiny. Add 2 if site under "nighttime conditions." Tauntaun lost if total destiny > 5. Other creature vehicle lost if total destiny > 3.

Title: Surface Defense Cannon
Gametext: Use 1 Force to deploy on your starfighter, free on Falcon. May target a character or creature at same site using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit if destiny +1 > defense value.

Title: Tactical Support
Gametext: Lose 1 Force to take up to three troopers into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Tamizander Rey
Gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Your starships may move from same exterior site for free. While at Echo Docking Bay, once every turn, may allow one character on Hoth to be immune to The Shield Doors Must Be Closed.

Title: Target The Main Generator
Gametext:
During your control phase, fire your AT-AT Cannon (if within range of the Main Power Generators) as follows:
Prepare To Target The Main Generator: Draw destiny.
Maximum Firepower!: If (destiny + X + Y) > 8, Main Power Generators site is "blown away" and this card is lost. Otherwise this card is used.
X = ability of one of AT-AT's pilots.
Y = total Hoth sites you control.

Title: Tauntaun
Gametext: May add 1 'rider' (passenger). Deploy only on Hoth. Ability = ¼. May move as a 'react' from a battle. May be 'sacrificed' (lost) to make rider immune to Exposure this turn.

Title: Tauntaun Bones
Gametext: Use 1 Force to deploy on table. Each opponent's destiny draw, you do the following: (0) Put top used card in hand; (1) lose 1 Force. (2) activate 1 Force; (3) lose this Effect; (4) retrieve 1 Force; (5) deploy a character for free; (6+) nothing.

Title: Tauntaun Handler
Gametext: Adds 2 to power of any creature vehicle he rides. When riding a tauntaun, also draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.

Title: That's It, The Rebels Are There!
Gametext: If you have a probe droid at a site during your control phase, move one of your starships to the related system. That starship cannot move again this turn.

Title: The First Transport Is Away!
Gametext: Deploy on any system (except Hoth). Target a Medium Transport at a Hoth site. When reached by target: Retrieve X Force, where X = twice the number of passengers. Relocate Utinni Effect to Hoth system. Your total power is +2 in battles at Hoth sites.

Title: The Shield Doors Must Be Closed
Gametext: Deploy between Echo Docking Bay and innermost marker site. When under "nighttime conditions," no movement is allowed to or from Echo Docking Bay unless it is to or from an Echo site.

Title: This Is Just Wrong
Gametext: Deploy on any male character. Target a female character. Target is power -2. Utinni Effect canceled when present with target.

Title: Tigran Jamiro
Gametext: Deploys only on Yavin 4 or Hoth. Opponent's aliens and Imperials may not move from same site as Tigran to an Echo or an interior Yavin site.

Title: Too Cold For Speeders
Gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy on your side of table. Each non-creature vehicle at marker sites under "nighttime conditions" is power = 0, maneuver = 0 and landspeed = 0.

Title: Toryn Farr
Gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything she pilots. When at any war room, adds 1 to weapon destiny draws of your Planet Defender Ion Cannon on same planet.

Title: Trample
Gametext: If you have a piloted AT-AT or AT-ST present at a site, target opponent's character, 'crashed' vehicle or unpiloted vehicle without armor present. Draw destiny. Character lost if destiny > ability. Vehicle lost if destiny < 7.

Title: Turn It Off! Turn It Off!
Gametext: USED: Cancel any attempt to place a 'hit' starship, vehicle or droid in the Used Pile rather than the Lost Pile. OR Cancel Han's Toolkit. LOST: Cancel Crash Site Memorial.

Title: Tyrant
Gametext: May add 6 pilots, 8 passengers, 2 vehicles and 4 TIEs. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. When using Tractor Beam, adds 1 to destiny draw.

Title: Under Attack
Gametext: During your control phase, target a vehicle with armor present with your warrior. Draw destiny. If warrior has a Concussion Grenade or a lightsaber, add 3 to destiny draw (7 if both). Vehicle (and grenade) lost if total destiny > armor.

Title: Vehicle Mine
Gametext: Deploy at same exterior site as your mining droid. 'Explodes' if starfighter (use 5 as defense value) or non-creature vehicle deploys or moves to or across same site. Draw destiny. Target lost if destiny +2 > defense value. Vehicle Mine is also lost.

Title: Vehicle Mine
Gametext: Deploy at same exterior site as your mining droid. 'Explodes' if starfighter (use 5 as defense value) or non-creature vehicle deploys or moves to or across same site. Draw destiny. Target lost if destiny +2 > defense value. Vehicle Mine is also lost.

Title: Walker Barrage
Gametext: If you have a piloted AT-AT present at a site, target opponent's artillery weapon at same or adjacent exterior site. Draw destiny. Target lost if destiny +1 > forfeit. Also, one opponent's character at same site as target (random selection) lost if destiny +1 > 6.

Title: Walker Sighting
Gametext: If opponent just moved or deployed an AT-AT to a planet site, deploy up to three exterior sites of that planet from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Wall Of Fire
Gametext: If you have a piloted AT-AT present at a site, target any number of opponent's troopers present at same or adjacent exterior site. Draw destiny. If destiny > number of troopers targeted, they are lost.

Title: Wampa
Gametext: * Ferocity = 3 + destiny. Habitat: Hoth sites. Deploy only to Wampa Cave or unoccupied marker site. Defeated characters are eaten or relocated to Wampa Cave (opponent of victim chooses).

Title: Weapon Malfunction
Gametext: Deploy on any docking bay. Target a weapon deployed on a starfighter or vehicle. That weapon cannot be fired. Utinni Effect canceled when reached by target.

Title: WED-1016 'Techie' Droid
Gametext: While at an exterior planet site or docking bay, once per turn may lose 1 Force to place a 'hit' starship or vehicle at same site, adjacent site, related system or related cloud sector in Used Pile instead of Lost Pile.

Title: Wes Janson
Gametext: Adds 1 to weapon destiny draws of anything he is aboard as a passenger (adds 3 if aboard Rogue 3 or with Wedge or Jek).

Title: Who's Scruffy-Looking?
Gametext: Cancel Scruffy-Looking Nerf Herder or I'd Just As Soon Kiss A Wookiee or Furry Fury or This Is Just Wrong or Death Mark or Mournful Roar or Takeel or Ket Maliss. OR Double Rennek's power for remainder of turn.

Title: Wyron Serper
Gametext: Once during each of your control phases, may peek at X cards randomly selected from opponent's hand, where X = number of (Dark Side Force icon) icons at same site. Also, when you are drawing destiny, adds 2 to the destiny of any card with 'scan' in the title.

Title: Yaggle Gakkle
Gametext: Target a creature vehicle at same site as a creature. If ferocity > target's maneuver + landspeed, creature vehicle is eaten, cumulatively adding 2 to creature's ferocity.

Title: You Have Failed Me For The Last Time
Gametext: If Vader is on table when opponent has just initiated a battle, target one opponent's leader of ability < 6 involved in that battle. If opponent does not win battle, target is forfeit = 0 and is lost (placed out of play if Ozzel).

Title: You Will Go To The Dagobah System
Gametext: During your control phase, use 1 Force to move any one of your [Hoth] icon characters of ability > 1 to any [Dagobah] icon location where you have presence. If moving to a Dagobah site, this movement is free and you do not need presence.

Title: Zev Senesca
Gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Rogue 2, also adds 3 to maneuver and may draw one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.

Title: Puck
Gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When choosing the destiny value of this card, must use 3 Force to choose 7. May deploy as a 'react.' Your Rebel pilots aboard snub fighters here are forfeit +1.

Title: Red 12
Gametext: May add 1 pilot. If Puck Naeco piloting, he may be placed in Used Pile instead of Lost Pile when he is forfeited. Immune to attrition < 4.

Title: Captain Khurgee
Gametext: While aboard Thunderflare\u0, attrition against you is -2 here. Once during your turn, if at a battleground, may peek at top card of opponent's Reserve Deck. If it is a character, may reveal it and opponent loses 1 Force (if it is a Rebel, may also place it on Used Pile).

Title: Boba Fett
Gametext: Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. Deploys -1 aboard Slave I. Adds one battle destiny with Vader (or while piloting Slave I). Once per game, if a battle was just initiated here, may exchange a card in hand with a card in Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Death Trooper
Gametext: While you have no other trooper here (except death troopers), adds one battle destiny at same site as Krennic, Tarkin, or Thrawn. May place this character in Used Pile to cancel a just drawn weapon destiny targeting your leader here.

Title: Veers
Gametext: Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. Leader. Once per game, if at a Hoth location, may take Prepare For A Surface Attack, a [Hoth] combat vehicle, or an exterior marker site into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Vader's Custom TIE
Gametext: May add 1 pilot. Non-[V0] Vader deploys -2 aboard. If Vader piloting, immune to attrition < 5, and once per battle, may cancel game text of opponent's pilot aboard a starfighter here.

Title: Xizor's Bounty
Gametext: Use 1 Force to deploy on opponent's just deployed character at same site as a Black Sun agent; character may not battle this turn. If character is about to leave table or be captured, peek at opponent's hand, retrieve 1 Force, and lose Immediate Effect.

Title: Any Methods Necessary
Gametext: If Jodo Kast or your Fett was just targeted by a weapon, cancel the targeting. Place weapon (unless [Permanent Weapon]) in owner's Used Pile. OR Take into hand (or deploy as a 'react') from Reserve deck: Binders, Jet Pack, Mandalorian Armor, or a blaster rifle; reshuffle.

Title: Bodhi Rook
Gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots, 3 if Rogue One or a stolen starship. May be deployed simultaneously with a piloted starship from hand to a system, even without presence or Force icons. If about to be lost, your Rebel or Rebel starship at a related location may make a regular move.

Title: Cal Alder
Gametext: May deploy as a 'react.' Deploys -1 to same site as a Rebel leader. Unless with Luke, opponent must first use 1 Force to fire a weapon at same site. Elis Helrot may not transport characters to or from here.

Title: Captain Cassian Andor
Gametext: Deploys -1 if a Rebel leader on table. Once per game, may place a character in your Lost Pile out of play to cancel a just drawn weapon or battle destiny here. If just lost, may activate 1 Force. While at opponent's location, immune to attrition < 4.

Title: Jyn Erso
Gametext: May deploy to a site as an Undercover spy. Draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise. If just lost, may peek at opponent's hand.

Title: K-2SO (Kay-Tuesso)
Gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise. While with Cassian, attrition against opponent is +1 here. If just lost, place out of play; if lost from a site, opponent may not move from there for remainder of turn.

Title: What Chance Do We Have?
Gametext: Deploy on table. Whenever you lose Force (except from a Force drain or your card) during opponent's control phase, unless opponent occupies more battlegrounds than you, may reduce loss (to a minimum of 1) by the number of battlegrounds you occupy. (Immune to Alter.)

Title: Rogue One
Gametext: May add 2 pilots and 4 passengers. May deploy with a pilot to a system without presence or Force icons. Spies deploy -1 aboard. Immune to attrition < 6 at opponent's system (unless a Dark Jedi here).

Title: The Falcon
Gametext: May add 2 pilots and 2 passengers. Once per game, during your move phase, may make an additional move. While [Episode VII] Chewie, [Episode VII] Han, or Rey piloting, maneuver = 6 and immune to attrition < 5.

Title: Ability, Ability, Ability
Gametext: Deploy on opponent's side of table. At the end of opponent's deploy phase, if they did not deploy a card with ability, opponent loses 2 Force. Effect lost if opponent has more cards with ability on table than you. (Immune to Alter.)

Title: Abyss
Gametext: Deploy on table. If a unique (•) card is drawn for destiny and a duplicate is on table, destiny card is lost (destiny = 0). If duplicated card is a character, it loses immunity to attrition for rest of turn and player must lose 2 Force or lose that character. (Immune to Alter.)

Title: Access Denied
Gametext: Insert face up in your Reserve Deck. When Effect reaches top it is lost, along with all opponent's 'insert' cards there. Reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.) OR Deploy between two mobile sites. Opponent's characters may pass only if aboard a Lift Tube or opponent uses +1 Force each.

Title: Advantage
Gametext: If an opponent's character of ability > 3 was just lost in a battle or duel you won, deploy on one of your warriors involved. Warrior is power +2. During each of opponent's move phases, opponent loses 1 Force (2 if character was a Dark Jedi). (Immune to Control.)

Title: Aiiii! Aaa! Agggggggggg!
Gametext: If you have a Rebel of ability > 1 captive at a prison you control, opponent loses X Force, where X = the number of opponent's characters with ability > 2 on table.

Title: All My Urchins
Gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy at any site where you have presence. Moves like a single character at normal use of the Force. Before initiating a battle where present, a player must first lose 2 Force. Effect lost if you initiate a battle where present.

Title: All Too Easy
Gametext: If an opponent's character at the Carbonite Chamber was just 'hit' by a lightsaber, deploy on that character. Character is instead immediately captured and 'frozen.' If captive released, lose Immediate Effect. (Immune to Control.)

Title: Ambush
Gametext: During your turn, target a site where your total power is more than double opponent's total power. Unless opponent has a Dark Jedi or character weapon there, place each opponent's character, vehicle and starship there (and cards on them) in owner's Used Pile.

Title: Armed And Dangerous
Gametext: If a battle or duel was just initiated at a site, deploy (for free) a unique matching weapon on one of your participating characters from hand or Reserve Deck; reshuffle (if from Reserve Deck).

Title: Artoo, Come Back At Once!
Gametext: USED: Search your Reserve Deck, take one Hero Of A Thousand Devices into hand and reshuffle. LOST: If R2-D2 is lost, use 1 Force to retrieve him. OR Use 3 Force to search your Reserve Deck, take R2-D2 into hand and reshuffle.

Title: As Good As Gone
Gametext: During your move phase, use 2 Force to return one of your smugglers, gamblers or thieves on table (unless captured or missing) to your hand.

Title: Atmospheric Assault
Gametext: If you just initiated a battle at a Cloud City sector, add one battle destiny. OR During your deploy phase, deploy one TIE Assault Squadron for free (no replacement is necessary).

Title: Beldon's Eye
Gametext: Deploy on Bespin: Cloud City. Your Tibanna Gas Miners deploy free to Cloud City sites and double the Force they activate.

Title: Bespin
DarkSideText: If you control, opponent's characters and vehicles deploy +1 to Cloud City locations.
LightSideText: If you control, your characters and vehicles deploy -1 to Cloud City locations.

Title: Bespin
DarkSideText: If you control, your characters and vehicles deploy -1 to Cloud City locations.
LightSideText: If you control, opponent's characters and vehicles deploy +1 to Cloud City locations.

Title: Bespin: Cloud City
DarkSideText: If you control, for each of your starships or vehicles here, your total power is +1 in battles at Cloud City sites.
LightSideText: If you control, for each of your starships or vehicles here, your total power is +1 in battles at Cloud City sites.

Title: Bespin: Cloud City
DarkSideText: If you control, for each of your starships or vehicles here, your total power is +1 in battles at Cloud City sites.
LightSideText: If you control, for each of your starships or vehicles here, your total power is +1 in battles at Cloud City sites.

Title: Binders
Gametext: Deploy on one of your warriors or bounty hunters. May now escort any number of captives. If device removed from your character, select one captive escorted by that character to remain and release all others.

Title: Bionic Hand
Gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy on a Disarmed character. Cancels the disarming card. Character is power +1 and adds 1 to weapon destiny when firing character weapons. Device lost if character Disarmed again (otherwise, may not be removed).

Title: Blasted Droid
Gametext: During your control phase, fire (for free) one of your blasters carried by a trooper or one of your automated weapons. Any 'hit' targets are immediately lost.

Title: Blaster Proficiency
Gametext: USED: If you just targeted with a blaster, add 3 to your weapon destiny. LOST: Lose 1 Force to cause one opponent's character just 'hit' to be immediately placed in Lost Pile. OR Cancel Levitation Attack.

Title: Boba Fett
Gametext: Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Slave I, also adds 2 to maneuver and may draw one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. When escorting a captive, captive is forfeit +5. May 'fly' (landspeed = 3). Immune to attrition < 3.

Title: Boba Fett's Blaster Rifle
Gametext: Use 1 Force to deploy on Boba Fett, or 3 on your other bounty hunter. May deploy as a 'react.' May target a character, creature or vehicle using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Add 1 if targeting a vehicle. Target hit if total destiny > defense value. May fire repeatedly for 1 Force each time.

Title: Bounty
Gametext: Deploy on an opponent's non-droid character. If subsequently captured by a bounty hunter and then transferred to a prison, retrieve Force equal to character's forfeit -2 and place Effect in Used Pile. (Immune to Alter.)

Title: Brief Loss Of Control
Gametext: Just after the weapons phase of a battle, use 2 Force to cause each player to target one of that player's characters involved in the battle. Target characters cannot apply their ability toward drawing battle destiny this turn.

Title: Bright Hope
Gametext: May add 1 pilot and 6 passengers. Deploys and moves like a starfighter. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1.

Title: Captain Bewil
Gametext: During your control phase, may search your Reserve Deck, take one Laser Gate, Heart Of The Chasm or Rite Of Passage into hand and reshuffle. Opponent's characters may not move from same site as Bewil to a mobile site.

Title: Captain Han Solo
Gametext: Deploys only on Falcon, Hoth or Cloud City. Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Falcon, adds one battle destiny and 2 to maneuver. Once during each battle, may use 2 Force to cancel one opponent's destiny just drawn and cause a re-draw.

Title: Captive Fury
Gametext: USED: Cancel Force drain bonus from IT-O this turn. LOST: During your battle phase, any of your escorted captives at same site may initiate and participate in one battle (they may not use weapons or devices and you may not voluntarily forfeit or relocate them).

Title: Captive Pursuit
Gametext: USED: If a battle was just initiated at a site, target a captive present. Captive released if you win battle. LOST: Cancel Aiiii! Aaa! Agggggggggg!, Sonic Bombardment, Interrogation Array, This Is Some Rescue or Special Delivery.

Title: Carbon-Freezing
Gametext: Deploy on Carbonite Chamber. During your control phase, may target one captive present. Draw destiny. If destiny < 5, captive lost. If destiny > 10, place on captive. Captive is 'frozen' and opponent loses 8 Force. If captive released, lose Effect. (Immune to Alter.)

Title: Carbonite Chamber Console
Gametext: Deploy on Carbonite Chamber. Adds 3 to Carbon-Freezing destiny. Also, once during each of your turns, you may use 1 Force to take one Ugnaught, Prepare The Chamber or Carbon-Freezing into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Chasm
Gametext: Deploy on table. If a unique (•) card is drawn for destiny and is duplicated on table, destiny card is lost (destiny = 0). If duplicated card is a character, it loses immunity to attrition for rest of turn and player must lose 2 Force or lose that character. (Immune to Alter.)

Title: Chief Retwin
Gametext: May use 3 Force to 'hide' (be excluded) from a battle. May use 2 Force to target one device or weapon present which deploys on a site. Draw destiny. If destiny > target's deploy cost, target is lost.

Title: Civil Disorder
Gametext: Deploy on opponent's side of table. At the end of opponent's deploy phase, if they did not deploy a card with ability, opponent loses 2 Force. Effect lost if opponent has more cards with ability on table than you. (Immune to Alter.)

Title: Clash Of Sabers
Gametext: Use 2 Force to target a character present with your warrior with a lightsaber. Target cannot move or battle until the end of your next turn. OR Use 1 Force to search your Reserve Deck, take one Uncontrollable Fury into hand and reshuffle. OR Cancel Presence Of The Force.

Title: Cloud Car
Gametext: May add 1 pilot or passenger. At cloud sectors, power +1, may deploy as a 'react' and may move and be targeted by weapons like a starfighter. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1.

Title: Cloud Car
Gametext: May add 1 pilot or passenger. At cloud sectors, power +1, may deploy as a 'react' and may move and be targeted by weapons like a starfighter. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 1.

Title: Cloud City Blaster
Gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy on your warrior at a Cloud City site. May target a character or creature using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit (and may not be used to satisfy attrition) if destiny > defense value.

Title: Cloud City Blaster
Gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy on your warrior at a Cloud City site. May target a character or creature using 2 Force. Draw destiny. Target hit (and may not be used to satisfy attrition) if destiny > defense value.

Title: Cloud City Engineer
Gametext: When present at a converted site, may use 2 Force to raise your site to the top. Also, when present at an opponent's site that has a Scomp link, your Force drains are +1 there. Ugnaughts deploy -1 to same Cloud City site.

Title: Cloud City Sabacc
Gametext: Requirements: a gambler, thief or smuggler on Cloud City. Wild cards (1-6): Lando and Weather Vane. Clone cards: Locations and Ugnaughts. (Gamblers may use clone cards as zeroes.) Stakes: One starfighter, weapon or device.

Title: Cloud City Sabacc
Gametext: Requirements: a gambler, thief or smuggler on Cloud City. Wild cards (1-6): Lando and Weather Vane. Clone cards: Locations and Ugnaughts. (Gamblers may use clone cards as zeroes.) Stakes: One starfighter, weapon or device.

Title: Cloud City Technician
Gametext: When present at a converted site, may use 2 Force to raise your site to the top. Also, when present at an opponent's site that has a Scomp link, your Force drains are +1 there.

Title: Cloud City Trooper
Gametext: Deploys only on Cloud City, but may move elsewhere. Power -1 when at a site other than a Cloud City site.

Title: Cloud City Trooper
Gametext: Deploys only on Cloud City, but may move elsewhere. Power -1 when at a site other than a Cloud City site.

Title: Cloud City: Carbonite Chamber
DarkSideText: If you control, add 2 to your Carbon-Freezing destiny.
LightSideText: If you occupy, subtract 2 from opponent's Carbon-Freezing destiny.

Title: Cloud City: Carbonite Chamber
DarkSideText: If you control, add 1 to your Carbon-Freezing destiny.
LightSideText: If you control, Force drain +1 here and may cancel Carbon-Freezing here.

Title: Cloud City: Chasm Walkway
DarkSideText: If Weather Vane on table, characters about to be 'hit' here are relocated there.
LightSideText: If Weather Vane on table, characters about to be 'hit' here are relocated there.

Title: Cloud City: Chasm Walkway
DarkSideText: If Weather Vane on table, characters about to be 'hit' here are relocated there.
LightSideText: If Weather Vane on table, characters about to be 'hit' here are relocated there.

Title: Cloud City: Dining Room
DarkSideText: Your characters and character weapons may deploy here as a 'react.'
LightSideText: If you control, Blue Milk, Beru Stew and Yoda Stew are doubled. Jek is deploy -2 here.

Title: Cloud City: East Platform (Docking Bay)
DarkSideText: Your docking bay transit from here requires 1 Force.
LightSideText: Your docking bay transit from here requires 2 Force.

Title: Cloud City: Guest Quarters
DarkSideText: If you control, Force drain -1 here.
LightSideText: Leia is deploy -2 here

Title: Cloud City: Incinerator
DarkSideText: If you control, during your control phase, may use 2 Force to retrieve one droid.
LightSideText: If you control, Force drain -1 here.

Title: Cloud City: Incinerator
DarkSideText: If you control without an Ugnaught, Force drain -1 here.
LightSideText: If you occupy, during your control phase, may use 3 Force to retrieve one droid.

Title: Cloud City: Lower Corridor
DarkSideText: Your characters with lightsabers are each power +2 here.
LightSideText: If you control, Force drain -1 here.

Title: Cloud City: Lower Corridor
LightSideText: Your characters with lightsabers are each power +2 here.

Title: Cloud City: Platform 327 (Docking Bay)
DarkSideText: Your docking bay transit from here requires 2 Force.
LightSideText: Your docking bay transit from here requires 1 Force.

Title: Cloud City: Security Tower
DarkSideText: Once per game, may search your Reserve Deck, take Lando into hand and reshuffle.
LightSideText: If you control, instead of Force draining, may release one captive here.

Title: Cloud City: Upper Plaza Corridor
DarkSideText: During your move phase, you may move free between here and any Cloud City site.
LightSideText: If you control, Force drain +1 here.

Title: Cloud City: Upper Plaza Corridor
DarkSideText: If you control, Force drain +1 here.
LightSideText: During your move phase, you may move free between here and any Cloud City site.

Title: Clouds
DarkSideText: If you control, once per turn, may add 1 to a Force drain at a related site. Starships are power and maneuver -2 here.
LightSideText: If you control, Force drain +1 here. Starships are power and maneuver -2 here.

Title: Clouds
DarkSideText: If you control, Force drain +1 here. Starships are power and maneuver -2 here.
LightSideText: If you control, once per turn, may add 1 to a Force drain at a related site. Starships are power and maneuver -2 here.

Title: Commander Desanne
Gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Your shuttling, landing and taking off to or from same location is free. During your control phase may take one Lambda shuttle or Landing Craft into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.

Title: Computer Interface
Gametext: USED: Cancel Limited Resources. LOST: Use 2 Force (free if Lobot on table) to examine the top card of your Reserve Deck, Force Pile and Used Pile. Return one of those three cards to the top of each deck or pile.

Title: Courage Of A Skywalker
Gametext: One of your Skywalkers present during a battle at a site, for remainder of turn, loses immunity to attrition but adds ability to power (he or she may not apply ability toward drawing battle destiny). OR During a duel, add one destiny to your total.

Title: Crack Shot
Gametext: Use 3 Force to deploy on table. Any card which is 'hit' may not be used to satisfy attrition. (Immune to Alter.)

Title: Cyborg Construct
Gametext: Deploy on an alien of ability < 3. Each turn, you may 'store' one card from hand face-down here. Holds up to three cards (six on Lobot). You may play or deploy cards from here as if from hand. Place stored cards in Used Pile if device lost or removed from character.

Title: Dark Approach
Gametext: If opponent just initiated a battle, you may do one of the following: Add one destiny to your total power only. OR If you have a character weapon present, select one opponent's character present to lose all immunity to attrition for remainder of battle.

Title: Dark Deal
Gametext: Deploy on Bespin: Cloud City if you control that sector and at least three related sites. At each Cloud City site, your total power is +4 and your Force drains are +2. Effect canceled if opponent occupies four Bespin locations. (Immune to Alter.)

Title: Dark Strike
Gametext: If you just targeted with a lightsaber, add 3 to your weapon destiny. OR Cancel Swing-And-A-Miss. OR Lose 1 Force to cause one opponent's character just 'hit' to be immediately placed in Lost Pile.

Title: Dash
Gametext: Use 2 Force to increase a character's or creature vehicle's landspeed by 1 for remainder of turn. OR Use 3 Force to move one of your characters as a 'react' (free if character is a scout).

Title: Despair
Gametext: If a Rebel was just captured or 'frozen,' deploy on another Rebel. That Rebel may not apply ability toward drawing battle destiny (if Leia, she is also excluded from being the "highest-ability character"). If captive released, lose Immediate Effect.

Title: Desperate Reach
Gametext: During your move phase, relocate one of your characters (unless Disarmed) from Weather Vane to any Cloud City site. Character may not move for remainder of turn. OR Cancel Imperial Barrier or The Shield Doors Must Be Closed.

Title: Dismantle On Sight
Gametext: Use 4 Force to deploy on a droid with armor (free on IG-88). At end of any opponent's turn, droid is immediately lost if present with an Imperial (or with a bounty hunter if droid is IG-88).

Title: Dodge
Gametext: If one of your characters of ability > 2 was just targeted by a weapon, subtract 3 from each weapon destiny draw. OR If opponent just initiated a battle at a site against one of your lone characters present, move that character away as a 'react' (for free).

Title: Double Back
Gametext: If a bounty hunter is lost, use 1 Force to retrieve one bounty hunter from your Lost Pile. OR Use 3 Force to search your Reserve Deck, take one bounty hunter into hand and reshuffle.

Title: Double-Crossing, No-Good Swindler
Gametext: If Han and your Lando are at same site, opponent loses 3 Force. OR If Nabrun Leids just completed a transport, Nabrun is lost and you may immediately deploy cards to that site from hand (at normal use of the Force, but troopers deploy free).

Title: E Chu Ta
Gametext: One of your protocol droids 'insults' one character present, canceling that character's game text for remainder of turn. OR During your battle phase, initiate a battle where both players have droids (but no presence or spies). Both sides add one battle destiny.

Title: E-3PO
Gametext: Total power at same site is +1 for each of your alien/Imperial pairs present. Once during every turn, may use 1 Force to 'insult' one opponent's droid present (except R2-D2), canceling that droid's game text for remainder of turn.

Title: End This Destructive Conflict
Gametext: USED: During a battle at a site, instead of firing one character weapon, cause one opponent's character present to be power -4 until end of turn. LOST: During a battle at a site, use 3 Force to cancel one battle destiny just drawn.

Title: Epic Duel
Gametext:
Deploy on your side of table. The Circle Is Now Complete or Vader's Obsession may be played to initiate an epic duel as follows: If Vader is present with specified target, each player draws two destiny (add 1 to each destiny draw if using a lightsaber). Add character's ability.
If Vader loses, place him out of play. You lose 6 Force (9 if dueling Luke).
If Obi-Wan loses, place him out of play. Opponent loses 9 Force.
If Luke loses, opponent must choose: Cross Luke to the Dark Side and lose X Force, where X = Luke's ability. OR Lose Luke and lose triple X Force.

Title: Fall Of The Empire
Gametext: At the end of a battle that you won at an interior site where you have a character of ability > 3 present, relocate one opponent's character present to an adjacent site. (If on Cloud City, character may be relocated to Weather Vane instead.)

Title: Fall Of The Legend
Gametext: If you just lost a character during a battle or a duel at a Cloud City site, use 2 Force to relocate that character to Weather Vane instead of your Lost Pile. OR Search your Reserve Deck, take one Weather Vane into hand and reshuffle.

Title: Flight Escort
Gametext: During your move phase, if you have at least two combat vehicles at same cloud sector, relocate one starfighter present to a related docking bay or system. OR If one of your combat vehicles is defending a battle at a cloud sector, add one battle destiny.

Title: Focused Attack
Gametext: If Vader is present during a battle at a site, for remainder of turn, he loses his immunity to attrition, but adds ability to power (he may not apply ability toward drawing battle destiny). OR During a duel, add one destiny to your total.

Title: Force Field
Gametext: USED: Cancel an attempt to target a Dark Jedi with a character weapon. LOST: If one of your characters was just targeted by a weapon during a battle, use 3 Force to cancel the targeting.

Title: Forced Landing
Gametext: Deploy on a docking bay. Target an opponent's starfighter at the related system or a related cloud sector. Target may not move away from Utinni Effect. Utinni Effect canceled when reached by target.

Title: Frozen Assets
Gametext: Deploy on your side of table. At every site where there is a 'frozen' captive, your Rebels deploy -2 and are power +2 in battle. OR Deploy on top of opponent's Force Pile. Force below this card may not be drawn or used. Effect lost at end of opponent's next turn.

Title: Gambler's Luck
Gametext: If any gambler is defending a battle alone at a site, add one battle destiny (draw two destiny and choose one). OR If your Lando is defending a battle alone at a site, add two battle destiny (draw three and choose two).

Title: Glancing Blow
Gametext: If you have a character with a lightsaber present in a battle with Vader, lose 1 Force to reduce Vader's power to zero. OR If you have a character with a lightsaber in a duel, cancel one opponent's destiny draw immediately after it is revealed.

Title: Haven
Gametext: Deploy on one of the following systems: Rendezvous Point, Hoth, Yavin 4, Alderaan, or Sullust. Your starships deploy -2 and your pilots deploy -1 here. When battling here, you may add one battle destiny. Effect canceled if opponent controls this system. (Immune to Alter.)

Title: He's All Yours, Bounty Hunter
Gametext: USED: Cancel Captive Pursuit. LOST: During your move phase, transfer an escorted captive to another bounty hunter or warrior present.

Title: Heart Of The Chasm
Gametext: During your deploy phase, use X Force to rearrange all Cloud City sites, where X = total number of those sites. All cards at a given site move along with that site. OR Cancel Off The Edge. OR Search your Reserve Deck, take one Weather Vane into hand and reshuffle.

Title: Hero Of A Thousand Devices
Gametext: Deploy on one of your droids. During your deploy phase, may use 1 Force to search your Reserve Deck, take one device that deploys on a droid into hand and reshuffle. Also, you may forfeit devices deployed on this droid (forfeit value = destiny number).

Title: Higher Ground
Gametext: USED: During a battle at a site, instead of firing one character weapon, cause one opponent's character present to be power -4 until end of turn. LOST: During a battle at a site, use 3 Force to cancel one battle destiny just drawn.

Title: Hindsight
Gametext: Deploy on C-3PO. Eyes In The Dark, The Professor, Mantellian Savrip and Hopping Mad are immune to Alter. Once during each draw phase, unless C-3PO is present with a Wookiee, you may examine the cards in your Used Pile. (Immune to Alter.)

Title: Hopping Mad
Gametext: Deploy on one of your droids. During your control phase, may use 1 Force to search your Reserve Deck; take one Droid Shutdown, The Professor, We're Doomed, Scomp Link Access, This Is All Your Fault or Shocking Information into hand and reshuffle.

Title: Human Shield
Gametext: USED: If an opponent's weapon just 'hit' an Imperial present with a captive being escorted, the captive is 'hit' instead. LOST: During a battle at a site, you may forfeit any or all captives present (once per battle per captive).

Title: I Am Your Father
Gametext: If Vader just won a battle or duel against a Luke of ability < 6, deploy on Luke. During each of your move phases, opponent loses 2 Force. Also, when at same location as Vader, Luke is power and forfeit = 0 and does not add power to any starships he pilots.

Title: I Don't Need Their Scum, Either
Gametext: USED: Search your Reserve Deck, take one We Don't Need Their Scum into hand and reshuffle. LOST: If a bounty hunter and your Lando are involved in the same battle, you may add one battle destiny (add two if bounty hunter is Boba Fett).

Title: I Had No Choice
Gametext: Deploy on an opponent's gambler. Cancels gambler's game text. If a battle was just initiated, you may use X Force to exclude gambler from that battle, where X = gambler's ability.

Title: Imperial Decree
Gametext: Deploy on your side of table. Whenever you control any two Rebel Base locations, or any one planet site and two systems, the effects of Revolution and all opponent's Force drain bonuses are canceled. (Immune to Alter.)

Title: Imperial Trooper Guard Dainsom
